ological scales. In this topical review, we aim to provide the\nstate-of-the-art supporting the development of a network theoretic approach as\na promising tool for understanding BCIs and improve usability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Jun 2020 17:39:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Jun 2020 17:22:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 11 Feb 2021 13:18:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-12"}
