 a small portion of FSRQs.The corona-jet,\ndisk-corona, and disk-jet connections of RLQs are likely driven by independent\nphysical processes. Furthermore, the corona-jet connection implies that\nsmall-scale processesin the vicinity of SMBHs, probably associated with the\nmagnetic flux/topology instead of black-hole spin, are controlling the\nradio-loudness of quasars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Jun 2020 18:00:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-25"}
