 transit capacity restriction\npolicy during reopening needs to be accompanied by (1) support for\nmicromobility modes, particularly in non-Manhattan boroughs, and (2) congestion\nalleviation policies that focus on reducing traffic in Manhattan, such as\ncordon-based pricing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Jun 2020 22:46:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Feb 2021 05:14:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-30"}
